Package com.sharneng.lookup

Generic Reference Lookup Solution.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Converter<TFrom,TTo>
    Interface to convert from one object to another.
    Lookup<T>
    The primary interface to support lookup of a object by some index.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLookup<T>
    A convenient abstract class that helps to implement Lookup interface.
    Lookups
    Class to hold factory methods to return the implementation of Lookup.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateKeyException
    Indicates an error where same sets of keys resolves to two or more different values when building a lookup.
    LookupBuildException
    Exception to indicate an error in building a lookup
    LookupException
    Exception to indicate an error looking up a value from and instance of Lookup.
